question: Where can I find restaurant heading towards the Last House on Mulholland, Los Angeles, CA from Monrovia Canyon Park, Monrovia, CA, within a radius of 150 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-117.988399 34.176394)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.320457 34.131243)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-117.988399 34.176394)',4326)::geography, 150000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-117.988399 34.176394)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
